newsitem.title: TUNISIA: Tunis bourse index closes up in higher trade.
newsitem.headline: Tunis bourse index closes up in higher trade.

text.p: The Tunis Stock Exchange on Wednesday closed up by 2.05 points in higher trade, bourse sources said.
The market's 30-share index closed at 594.91 from 592.86 on Tuesday.
Trade volume was 2.57 million dinars against 1.22 million dinars. Exchanges on the bond's market amounted to 913,517 dinars.
BIAT bank was up 1.83 dinar to 63.13 dinars. AMEN bank won 1.61 dinar to 55.56 dinars. Coke bottler SFBT was up 3.56 dinar to 118.7 dinars.
